Package: reviewer
Title: Interactive LLM-Powered Tidy Code Review
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Simon", "Couch", , "simon.couch@posit.co", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5676-5107"))
Description: Provides an interactive Shiny application for reviewing R code with
    AI assistance. An LLM suggests edits to improve reproducibility, readability,
    and resilience which you can choose to accept or reject. Changes are applied directly
    to your file.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
